				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the pronunciation characteristic of a particular group of people relative to another group.  For the prominence of a syllable, see <a href="Accent_(phonetics)" title="Accent (phonetics)">accent (phonetics)</a>.  For the symbols on letters, see <a href="Diacritic" title="Diacritic">diacritic</a>.</div>
<div class="dablink">For other uses, see <a href="Accent_(disambiguation)" title="Accent (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Accent (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
